{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1519,"text":"What I'm going to do is to just give a few notes,"},{"time":4294,"text":"and this is from a book I'm preparing called"},{"time":8110,"text":"\"Letters to a Young Scientist.\""},{"time":10535,"text":"I'd thought it'd be appropriate to"},{"time":12686,"text":"present it, on the basis that I have had extensive experience"},{"time":17775,"text":"in teaching, counseling scientists across a broad array of fields."},{"time":21471,"text":"And you might like to hear some of the principles that I've developed in doing"},{"time":26870,"text":"that teaching and counseling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28551,"text":"So let me begin by urging you,"},{"time":31449,"text":"particularly you on the youngsters' side,"},{"time":33998,"text":"on this path you've chosen,"},{"time":35974,"text":"to go as far as you can."},{"time":37878,"text":"The world needs you, badly."},{"time":41346,"text":"Humanity is now fully into the techno-scientific age."},{"time":45864,"text":"There is going to be no turning back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":48343,"text":"Although varying among disciplines -- say, astrophysics,"},{"time":53268,"text":"molecular genetics, the immunology, the microbiology, the public"},{"time":57230,"text":"health, to the new area of the human body as a symbiont,"},{"time":63424,"text":"to public health, environmental science."},{"time":65905,"text":"Knowledge in medical science and science overall"},{"time":69021,"text":"is doubling every 15 to 20 years."},{"time":72158,"text":"Technology is increasing at a comparable rate."},{"time":75246,"text":"Between them, the two already pervade,"},{"time":78230,"text":"as most of you here seated realize,"},{"time":81094,"text":"every dimension of human life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83479,"text":"So swift is the velocity of the techno-scientific revolution,"},{"time":88535,"text":"so startling in its countless twists and turns, that no one can predict"},{"time":93262,"text":"its outcome even a decade from the present moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97710,"text":"There will come a time, of course,"},{"time":99407,"text":"when the exponential growth of discovery and knowledge,"},{"time":103158,"text":"which actually began in the 1600s,"},{"time":105294,"text":"has to peak and level off,"},{"time":108110,"text":"but that's not going to matter to you."},{"time":109358,"text":"The revolution is going to continue"},{"time":110672,"text":"for at least several more decades."},{"time":113630,"text":"It'll render the human condition"},{"time":115374,"text":"radically different from what it is today."},{"time":117720,"text":"Traditional fields of study are going to continue to grow"},{"time":124038,"text":"and in so doing, inevitably they will meet and create new disciplines."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128863,"text":"In time, all of science will come to be"},{"time":132710,"text":"a continuum of description, an explanation of networks, of principles and laws."},{"time":138166,"text":"That's why you need not just be training"},{"time":141366,"text":"in one specialty, but also acquire breadth in other fields,"},{"time":145806,"text":"related to and even distant from your own initial choice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149494,"text":"Keep your eyes lifted and your head turning."},{"time":153439,"text":"The search for knowledge is in our genes."},{"time":156504,"text":"It was put there by our distant ancestors"},{"time":160016,"text":"who spread across the world,"},{"time":161639,"text":"and it's never going to be quenched."},{"time":163334,"text":"To understand and use it sanely,"},{"time":166527,"text":"as a part of the civilization yet to evolve"},{"time":170486,"text":"requires a vastly larger population of scientifically trained people like you."},{"time":176328,"text":"In education, medicine, law, diplomacy,"},{"time":180366,"text":"government, business and the media that exist today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184654,"text":"Our political leaders need at least a modest degree of scientific"},{"time":189614,"text":"literacy, which most badly lack today --"},{"time":192710,"text":"no applause, please."},{"time":194254,"text":"It will be better for all"},{"time":196712,"text":"if they prepare before entering office rather than learning on the job."},{"time":201383,"text":"Therefore you will do well to act on the side,"},{"time":204542,"text":"no matter how far into the laboratory"},{"time":207247,"text":"you may go, to serve as teachers"},{"time":210566,"text":"during the span of your career."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212574,"text":"I'll now proceed quickly,"},{"time":214649,"text":"and before else, to a subject that is both a vital asset"},{"time":217838,"text":"and a potential barrier to a scientific career."},{"time":221270,"text":"If you are a bit short in mathematical skills,"},{"time":224750,"text":"don't worry."},{"time":226079,"text":"Many of the most successful scientists"},{"time":228590,"text":"at work today are mathematically semi-literate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232790,"text":"A metaphor will serve here:"},{"time":235275,"text":"Where elite mathematicians and statisticians"},{"time":241278,"text":"and theorists often serve as architects in the expanding realm"},{"time":246343,"text":"of science, the remaining large majority of"},{"time":250046,"text":"basic applied scientists, including a large portion of those who could be"},{"time":254758,"text":"said to be of the first rank, are the ones who map the terrain, they scout"},{"time":260110,"text":"the frontiers, they cut the pathways,"},{"time":262862,"text":"they raise the buildings along the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265598,"text":"Some may have considered me foolhardy,"},{"time":268774,"text":"but it's been my habit to brush aside the fear of mathematics"},{"time":272535,"text":"when talking to candidate scientists."},{"time":274598,"text":"During 41 years of teaching biology at Harvard,"},{"time":278398,"text":"I watched sadly as bright students turned away"},{"time":282515,"text":"from the possibility of a scientific career"},{"time":285439,"text":"or even from taking non-required courses in science"},{"time":289167,"text":"because they were afraid of failure."},{"time":290998,"text":"These math-phobes deprive science and medicine"},{"time":294358,"text":"of immeasurable amounts of badly needed talent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297607,"text":"Here's how to relax your anxieties, if you have them:"},{"time":301558,"text":"Understand that mathematics is a language"},{"time":304150,"text":"ruled like other verbal languages,"},{"time":307974,"text":"or like verbal language generally, by its own grammar"},{"time":310973,"text":"and system of logic."},{"time":312878,"text":"Any person with average quantitative intelligence"},{"time":315736,"text":"who learns to read and write mathematics"},{"time":318878,"text":"at an elementary level will, as in verbal language, have little difficulty"},{"time":325630,"text":"picking up most of the fundamentals"},{"time":327694,"text":"if they choose to master the mathspeak of most disciplines of science."}]},{"cues":[{"time":333031,"text":"The longer you wait to become at least semi-literate"},{"time":336814,"text":"the harder the language of mathematics will be to master, just as again in any verbal"},{"time":342822,"text":"language, but it can be done at any age."},{"time":345799,"text":"I speak as an authority"},{"time":347510,"text":"on that subject, because I'm an extreme case."},{"time":351361,"text":"I didn't take algebra until my freshman year"},{"time":355022,"text":"at the University of Alabama."},{"time":357053,"text":"They didn't teach it before then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359374,"text":"I finally got around to calculus as a 32-year-old tenured professor at Harvard,"},{"time":364278,"text":"where I sat uncomfortably in classes with undergraduate students,"},{"time":368904,"text":"little more than half my age."},{"time":371334,"text":"A couple of them were students"},{"time":372806,"text":"in a course I was giving on evolutionary biology."},{"time":376062,"text":"I swallowed my pride, and I learned calculus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381318,"text":"I found out that in science and all its applications,"},{"time":384414,"text":"what is crucial is not that technical ability,"},{"time":388376,"text":"but it is imagination in all of its applications."},{"time":391545,"text":"The ability to form concepts with images of entities and processes"},{"time":395879,"text":"pictured by intuition."},{"time":398815,"text":"I found out that advances in science rarely come upstream"},{"time":403159,"text":"from an ability to stand at a blackboard"},{"time":406191,"text":"and conjure images from unfolding mathematical propositions"},{"time":409326,"text":"and equations."},{"time":411182,"text":"They are instead the products of downstream imagination leading to hard work,"},{"time":416614,"text":"during which mathematical reasoning may or may not prove to be relevant."},{"time":421174,"text":"Ideas emerge when a part of the real or imagined world is studied"},{"time":426373,"text":"for its own sake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427790,"text":"Of foremost importance is a thorough, well-organized knowledge"},{"time":433431,"text":"of all that is known of the relevant entities and processes that might be involved in that domain"},{"time":440080,"text":"you propose to enter."},{"time":441520,"text":"When something new is discovered,"},{"time":443646,"text":"it's logical then that one of the follow-up steps is"},{"time":448615,"text":"to find the mathematical and statistical methods to move its analysis forward."},{"time":452767,"text":"If that step proves too difficult for"},{"time":455319,"text":"the person or team that made the discovery,"},{"time":459491,"text":"a mathematician can then be added by them"},{"time":464790,"text":"as a collaborator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467087,"text":"Consider the following principle,"},{"time":469246,"text":"which I will modestly call Wilson's Principle Number One:"},{"time":474446,"text":"It is far easier for scientists"},{"time":478846,"text":"including medical researchers, to require needed collaboration"},{"time":483415,"text":"in mathematics and statistics"},{"time":485533,"text":"than it is for mathematicians and statisticians"},{"time":489214,"text":"to find scientists able to make use of their equations."},{"time":493310,"text":"It is important in choosing the direction to take in science"},{"time":497404,"text":"to find the subject at your level of competence that interests you deeply,"},{"time":503150,"text":"and focus on that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504790,"text":"Keep in mind, then, Wilson's Second Principle:"},{"time":509486,"text":"For every scientist, whether researcher, technician,"},{"time":514022,"text":"teacher, manager or businessman,"},{"time":517117,"text":"working at any level of mathematical competence,"},{"time":521104,"text":"there exists a discipline in science or medicine"},{"time":524558,"text":"for which that level is enough to achieve excellence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528494,"text":"Now I'm going to offer quickly"},{"time":531054,"text":"several more principles that will be useful"},{"time":533462,"text":"in organizing your education and career,"},{"time":536150,"text":"or if you're teaching, how you might"},{"time":540535,"text":"enhance your own teaching and counseling of young scientists."},{"time":545423,"text":"In selecting a subject in which to conduct original research,"},{"time":549222,"text":"or to develop world-class expertise,"},{"time":552422,"text":"take a part of the chosen discipline that is sparsely inhabited."},{"time":557750,"text":"Judge opportunity by how few other students and researchers"},{"time":562462,"text":"are on hand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563998,"text":"This is not to de-emphasize the essential requirement"},{"time":567648,"text":"of broad training, or the value of apprenticing yourself"},{"time":571087,"text":"in ongoing research to programs of high quality."},{"time":575550,"text":"It is important also to acquire older mentors within these successful"},{"time":580278,"text":"programs, and to make friends and colleagues of your age"},{"time":584166,"text":"for mutual support."},{"time":586022,"text":"But through it all, look for a way to break out,"},{"time":588710,"text":"to find a field and subject not yet popular."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592646,"text":"We have seen this demonstrated already in the talks preceding mine."},{"time":596423,"text":"There is the quickest way advances are likely to occur,"},{"time":601534,"text":"as measured in discoveries per investigator per year."},{"time":605151,"text":"You may have heard the"},{"time":606758,"text":"military dictum for the gathering of armies:"},{"time":610518,"text":"March to the sound of the guns."},{"time":613239,"text":"In science, the exact opposite is the case: March away from the sound of the guns."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619749,"text":"So Wilson's Principle Number Three:"},{"time":622454,"text":"March away from the sound of the guns."},{"time":625798,"text":"Observe from a distance,"},{"time":627662,"text":"but do not join the fray."},{"time":629759,"text":"Make a fray of your own."},{"time":632127,"text":"Once you have settled on a specialty,"},{"time":636382,"text":"and the profession you can love, and you've secured opportunity,"},{"time":641662,"text":"your potential to succeed will be greatly enhanced if you study it"},{"time":646943,"text":"enough to become an expert."}]},{"cues":[{"time":649623,"text":"There are thousands of professionally delimited"},{"time":652950,"text":"subjects sprinkled through physics and chemistry"},{"time":655426,"text":"to biology and medicine."},{"time":657342,"text":"And on then into the social sciences,"},{"time":660238,"text":"where it is possible in short time to acquire"},{"time":663440,"text":"the status of an authority."},{"time":666014,"text":"When the subject is still very thinly populated,"},{"time":669526,"text":"you can with diligence and hard work become"},{"time":672147,"text":"the world authority."}]},{"cues":[{"time":674358,"text":"The world needs this kind of expertise,"},{"time":678319,"text":"and it rewards the kind of people"},{"time":680494,"text":"willing to acquire it."},{"time":682646,"text":"The existing information and what you self-discover"},{"time":687142,"text":"may at first seem skimpy and difficult to connect"},{"time":691253,"text":"to other bodies of knowledge."},{"time":693289,"text":"Well, if that's the case,"},{"time":695158,"text":"good. Why hard instead of easy?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":699300,"text":"The answer deserves to be stated as Principle Number Four."},{"time":704155,"text":"In the attempt to make scientific discoveries,"},{"time":707574,"text":"every problem is an opportunity,"},{"time":709567,"text":"and the more difficult the problem,"},{"time":711062,"text":"the greater will be the importance of its solution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713822,"text":"Now this brings me to a basic categorization"},{"time":717630,"text":"in the way scientific discoveries are made."},{"time":720505,"text":"Scientists, pure mathematicians among them,"},{"time":723869,"text":"follow one or the other of two pathways:"},{"time":727136,"text":"First through early discoveries,"},{"time":729246,"text":"a problem is identified"},{"time":731390,"text":"and a solution is sought."},{"time":733222,"text":"The problem may be relatively small;"},{"time":735751,"text":"for example, where exactly in a cruise ship does the norovirus begin to spread?"},{"time":741172,"text":"Or larger, what's the role of dark matter in the expansion of the universe?"},{"time":747078,"text":"As the answer is sought, other phenomena are typically discovered"},{"time":751537,"text":"and other questions are asked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753182,"text":"This first of the two strategies is like a hunter,"},{"time":756198,"text":"exploring a forest in search of a particular quarry,"},{"time":760447,"text":"who finds other quarries along the way."},{"time":763366,"text":"The second strategy of research"},{"time":766198,"text":"is to study a subject broadly"},{"time":767990,"text":"searching for unknown phenomena or patterns of known phenomena"},{"time":772766,"text":"like a hunter in what we call \"the naturalist's trance,\""},{"time":776567,"text":"the researcher of mind is open to anything interesting,"},{"time":780230,"text":"any quarry worth taking."},{"time":781614,"text":"The search is not for the solution of the problem,"},{"time":783967,"text":"but for problems themselves worth solving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787174,"text":"The two strategies of research,"},{"time":789166,"text":"original research, can be stated as follows,"},{"time":792351,"text":"in the final principle I'm going to offer you:"},{"time":796639,"text":"For every problem in a given discipline of science,"},{"time":800903,"text":"there exists a species or entity or phenomenon"},{"time":804478,"text":"ideal for its solution."},{"time":806424,"text":"And conversely, for every species or other entity"},{"time":811822,"text":"or phenomenon, there exist important problems"},{"time":814758,"text":"for the solution of which, those particular objects of research are ideally suited."},{"time":822335,"text":"Find out what they are."},{"time":824272,"text":"You'll find your own way to discover,"},{"time":827407,"text":"to learn, to teach."}]},{"cues":[{"time":829590,"text":"The decades ahead will see dramatic advances"},{"time":833023,"text":"in disease prevention, general health, the quality of life."},{"time":837590,"text":"All of humanity depends on the knowledge and practice of the medicine and the science"},{"time":843615,"text":"behind it you will master."},{"time":845198,"text":"You have chosen a calling that will come in steps"},{"time":848662,"text":"to give you satisfaction, at its conclusion, of a life well lived."},{"time":854073,"text":"And I thank you for having me here tonight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":856686,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":862054,"text":"Oh, thank you."},{"time":863326,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":870482,"text":"I salute you."}]}]}